The game met a highly positive reception, with several magazines giving the game their respective awards:

* [[Computer & Video Games]]: ''Game of the month''<ref>{{Cite book |url=http://archive.org/details/ComputerAndVideoGamesIssue053Mar86 |title=Computer And Video Games Issue 053 |date=March 1986 |language=English}}</ref>
* Crash Magazine: an overall rating of 93%, and the label of ''A Crash Smash''<ref name=":0" />
* [[Your Sinclair]]: a rating of 9 (out of 10), and the ''Megagame award''<ref>{{Cite book |url=http://archive.org/details/Your_Sinclair_003 |title=Your Sinclair #003 |date=March 1986 |year=1986 |pages=72–73 |language=en}}</ref>
* [[Sinclair User]] gave the game a ''SU Classic'' award

